    <h1>Old online store: Skrill</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Integration only for Callisto online stores</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This page only contains instructions for integrating <strong>Skrill</strong> in Callisto online stores. For further information on using <strong>Skrill</strong> in Ceres online stores, refer to the detailed information in the plugin description available in the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/plugins/payment/Skrill_5142" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentyMarketplace</a>.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The payment provider <a href="https://www.skrill.com/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Skrill</a> brings together a large number of <a href="/en/payment/payment-providers/skrill#40">payment methods</a> that are specific to particular countries.</p>
</div>
